### Search Manga with Filters
POST http://localhost:3000/api/manga/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "filters": [
        {
            "field": "year",
            "value": 2010,
            "action": "GREATER_THAN_OR_EQUALS",
            "score_multiplier": 1
        },
        {
            "field": "score",
            "value": 7.0,
            "action": "GREATER_THAN_OR_EQUALS",
            "score_multiplier": 1
        },
        {
            "field": "members",
            "value": 10000,
            "action": "GREATER_THAN_OR_EQUALS",
            "score_multiplier": 1
        },
        {
            "field": "genres",
            "value": ["Action", "Drama"],
            "action": "INCLUDES_ANY",
            "score_multiplier": {}
        },
        {
            "field": "status",
            "value": "Finished",
            "action": "EQUALS",
            "score_multiplier": 1
        }
    ],
    "hideWatched": ["Completed", "Avoiding"],
    "pagesize": 50,
    "sortBy": "score"
}


### Get Manga Statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/manga/stats

### Get Available Manga Fields
GET http://localhost:3000/api/manga/fields

### Get Available Filter Actions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/manga/filters

### Get Top Manga by Score
GET http://localhost:3000/api/manga/top?limit=50

### Get All Available Genres
GET http://localhost:3000/api/manga/genres

### Search by Type (Manga/Manhwa/Manhua)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/manga/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "filters": [
        {
            "field": "type",
            "value": "Manga",
            "action": "EQUALS",
            "score_multiplier": 1
        }
    ],
    "pagesize": 20
}

### Search by Chapters Count
POST http://localhost:3000/api/manga/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "filters": [
        {
            "field": "chapters",
            "value": 50,
            "action": "GREATER_THAN",
            "score_multiplier": 1
        },
        {
            "field": "chapters",
            "value": 200,
            "action": "LESS_THAN",
            "score_multiplier": 1
        }
    ],
    "pagesize": 25
}

