### Search Discontinued/On Hiatus Manga
POST http://localhost:3000/api/manga/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "filters": [
        {
            "field": "status",
            "value": ["Discontinued", "On Hiatus"],
            "action": "INCLUDES_ANY",
            "score_multiplier": {}
        }
    ],
    "pagesize": 10
}
